summary: This document is a summary of account balances and transactions for a business checking account at Deutsche Bank for the period from February 1, 2016, to February 29, 2016. It details various debits and credits, including preauthorized debits for payroll and health insurance, as well as checks paid during the month.
keyFacts: The account had a beginning balance of $560,347.24 on February 1, 2016.
